title: Bob Barker treated for cut to head after a sidewalk fall
text: > Entertainment Bob Barker treated for cut to head after a sidewalk fall FILE - In this Nov. 5, 2013 file photo, Bob Barker poses for a photo on the set of "The Price is Right" after a special appearance that will celebrate his 90th birthday at CBS Studios, in Los Angeles. Barker is resting at home after taking a fall on a Los Angeles street on Tuesday morning, Oct. 20, 2015. Barker's longtime friend and publicist, Henri Bollinger, said the former "The Price is Right‚Äù host suffered a cut to his head that required stitches, and a scraped leg.
